code: @Override public IndexResult index(Index index) throws IOException {     if (index.seqNo() != SequenceNumbers.UNASSIGNED_SEQ_NO) {         idToMaxSeqNo.compute(index.id(), (id, existing) -> {             if (existing == null) {                 return index.seqNo().             } else {                 long maxSeqNo = Math.max(index.seqNo(), existing).                 advanceMaxSeqNoOfUpdatesOrDeletes(maxSeqNo).                 return maxSeqNo.             }         }).     }     return super.index(index). }

@Override public DeleteResult delete(Delete delete) throws IOException {     if (delete.seqNo() != SequenceNumbers.UNASSIGNED_SEQ_NO) {         final long maxSeqNo = idToMaxSeqNo.compute(delete.id(), (id, existing) -> {             if (existing == null) {                 return delete.seqNo().             } else {                 return Math.max(delete.seqNo(), existing).             }         }).         advanceMaxSeqNoOfUpdatesOrDeletes(maxSeqNo).     }     return super.delete(delete). }
